<p>This interview is included in a book too.<br>
<br>
Yasuhiko said that Arion included over 2000 cuts while Oshii's Angel's Egg had only 400 cuts.<br>
As an animator, Yasuhiko thought he couldn't request such long cuts. Oshii said that the busy director life in Urusei influenced his style.</p>
